        <item>
            <title>Jaguar Type 00 概念車登場，大膽新設計展現全電動化願景</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/jaguar-type-00/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=jaguar-type-00</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/03/jaguar-type-00/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 12:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[jaguar]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1278922</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Jaguar 先前公佈全新品牌形象，前衞設計引起網上不少討論，而最近採用這設計元素的概念車終於現身，與一直以來的風格截然不同。<br /><span id="more-1278922"></span></p><p>Jaguar 在邁阿密藝術週發表的全新概念車 Type 00，可説是他們以全新形象向全電動化轉型的預覽。據 Jaguar 表示，概念車體現了他們「生動而極具張力的現代主義」設計哲學，重新詮釋品牌創辦人「Copy Nothing」的理念。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278925" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/hero_imagery_16x9_bl-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/hero_imagery_16x9_bl-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/hero_imagery_16x9_bl.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvision_hero_to-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvision_hero_to-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvision_hero_to.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278927" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/hero_imagery_16x9_bl-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/hero_imagery_16x9_bl-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/hero_imagery_16x9_bl-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Type 00 採用為未來電動車系列而設的 Jaguar Electric Architecture 電動架構，外型融合修長引擎蓋、流線型車頂和船尾設計，配備 23 吋合金鈴。車廂採用蝴蝶門設計，搭配手工黃銅飾邊和懸浮式儀錶板，設計前衞獨特。配色方面則有向邁阿密 Art Deco 風格致敬的「Miami Pink」，以及體現英國傳承的「London Blue」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278928" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionscreende-694x300.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="300" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionscreende-694x300.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionscreende.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278929" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionint_sh04-694x300.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="300" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionint_sh04-694x300.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionint_sh04.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278930" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisiontotemins-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisiontotemins-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisiontotemins.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Jaguar 計劃在 2025 年底推出首款新世代量產電動車，預計為一款四門 GT 跑車，目標實現 WLTP 續航力 770 公里，快充 15 分鐘可增加 321 公里續航距離。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278931" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionfrontdet-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionfrontdet-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionfrontdet.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278932" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionwheel_pr-690x580.jpg" alt="" width="690" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionwheel_pr-690x580.jpg 690w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionwheel_pr.jpg 1071w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 690px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278933" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionleaperon-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionleaperon-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/designvisionleaperon.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Jaguar 首席外觀設計師 Constantino Segui Gilabert 表示：「Jaguar 絕不容許平庸。當您首次看到全新 Jaguar 時，它必須讓人感到驚嘆，像是從未見過的存在。Type 00 引人注目，就像過去所有出類拔萃的 Jaguar 一樣，並擁有強大的存在感，彰顯出獨特的英國創意與原創精神，讚揚藝術，體現了非凡現代主義的精髓。」</p><br /><b>
